Description

Reversible two pockets Top & one Pocket Scrub Pants with adjustable drawstring available for you to choose from. 65% Polyester 35% Cotton Machine washable cold to warm water with similar colors. Tumble dry on low. Product has a roomy fit. For more fitted results, one size smaller than your standard size is recommended for women only. For optimal fit for men, your standard size is recommended. Great for nurses, CNAs, vets, dental assistants, medical exams, science labs, med schools, nursing students, EMTs, doctors and dentist office, hospitals, etc.
